      <div class="about-layout">
        <div class="about-text reveal">
          <p class="about-lead">I'm an AI &amp; ML engineering student who builds things that think.</p>
          <p class="about-body">From designing constraint-based timetable systems to leading a multilingual street-sign transliteration tool for India, I gravitate toward problems where software meets real human needs. I scored a perfect 600/600 in my 10th class, 939/1000 in Intermediate, and currently hold an 8.4 CGPA — but what drives me more is shipping projects that actually work.</p>
        </div>
