            <h3 class="project-title" id="proj-lipis-title">Street Sign Transliteration Tool</h3>
            <p class="project-desc">Led the development of a multilingual street-sign transliteration pipeline, ranking in the Top 7 nationally at the Smart India Hackathon (SIH) 2024.</p>
            <div class="project-stack"><code>Deep Learning</code><code>Image Processing</code><code>Python</code><code>NLP</code></div>
