              View Repository ↗
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="project-card-accent" aria-hidden="true"><div class="accent-glyph">लि</div></div>
        </article>

        <div class="projects-secondary-grid">
          <article class="project-card reveal" aria-labelledby="proj-yolo-title">
            <div class="project-eyebrow"><span class="project-tag">Active Project · 2025</span></div>
            <img src="assets/BTech_E2E_Project_Logo.png" alt="Maize Disease Detector Logo" class="project-logo" />
            <h3 class="project-title" id="proj-yolo-title">Maize Disease Detector</h3>
            <p class="project-desc">End-to-end YOLO-based system for real-time maize disease detection from field images.</p>
            <div class="project-stack"><code>YOLO</code><code>Computer Vision</code><code>Python</code></div>
            <a href="https://github.com/AdhimulamBhargavSaiViswanath-05/Maize-Disease-Detector" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="proj-link">View Repository ↗</a>
          </article>
          <article class="project-card reveal" aria-labelledby="proj-tt-title">
            <div class="project-eyebrow"><span class="project-tag">Solo · 2025–2026</span><span class="project-tag project-tag-demo">Live Demo</span></div>
            <img src="assets/TimeTableGenerator_Logo.png" alt="AI Timetable Generator Logo" class="project-logo" />
            <h3 class="project-title" id="proj-tt-title">AI Timetable Generator</h3>
            <p class="project-desc">Constraint-based CSP that auto-generates conflict-free academic timetables with real-world scheduling constraints.</p>
            <div class="project-stack"><code>CSP</code><code>Python</code><code>AI</code></div>
            <a href="https://github.com/AdhimulamBhargavSaiViswanath-05/AI-Timetable-Generator" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="proj-link">GitHub ↗</a>
          </article>
          <article class="project-card reveal" aria-labelledby="proj-nlp-title">
            <div class="project-eyebrow"><span class="project-tag">Solo · 2025</span></div>
            <img src="assets/NLP_Logo.png" alt="NLP Stemming Engine Logo" class="project-logo" />
            <h3 class="project-title" id="proj-nlp-title">Custom NLP Stemming Engine</h3>
            <p class="project-desc">Rule-based stemming algorithm for text normalization, token processing, and root extraction.</p>
            <div class="project-stack"><code>NLP</code><code>Python</code><code>Text Processing</code></div>
            <a href="https://github.com/AdhimulamBhargavSaiViswanath-05/Custom-NLP-Stemming-Engine" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="proj-link">GitHub ↗</a>
          </article>
          <article class="project-card reveal" aria-labelledby="proj-bus-title">
            <div class="project-eyebrow"><span class="project-tag">Solo · 2024</span></div>
            <img src="assets/Bus_Price_Prediction.png" alt="Bus Service Prediction Logo" class="project-logo" />
            <h3 class="project-title" id="proj-bus-title">Bus Service Prediction</h3>
            <p class="project-desc">ML model predicting bus passenger demand and ticket pricing using feature selection and evaluation.</p>
            <div class="project-stack"><code>Scikit-learn</code><code>Pandas</code><code>ML</code></div>
            <a href="https://github.com/AdhimulamBhargavSaiViswanath-05/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="proj-link">GitHub ↗</a>
          </article>
          <article class="project-card reveal" aria-labelledby="proj-amz-title">
            <div class="project-eyebrow"><span class="project-tag">Solo · 2024</span></div>
            <img src="assets/Amazon_web_Scraping_Logo.png" alt="Amazon Trend Analysis Logo" class="project-logo" />
            <h3 class="project-title" id="proj-amz-title">Amazon Trend Analysis</h3>
            <p class="project-desc">Scraped Amazon product data and built Python visualizations to surface pricing and demand trends.</p>
            <div class="project-stack"><code>BeautifulSoup</code><code>Pandas</code><code>Matplotlib</code></div>
            <a href="https://github.com/AdhimulamBhargavSaiViswanath-05/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="proj-link">GitHub ↗</a>
